vote.title:
16.Agreement with Mekong Printing Inc. dba MK Printing for Offset Printing 
Services (Specification No. 24-082A) (General Fund and Non -General Fund)
vote.description:
Department(s): Finance and Management Services 
Recommended Action: Authorize the City Manager to execute an agreement with 
Mekong Printing Inc. dba MK Printing to provide offset printing services for a term 
beginning November 20, 2024 and expiring November 19, 2027, with provision for 
one, 2-year extension, in an amount not to exceed $500,000 (Agreement No. A- 
2024-207). 
MINUTES: Mayor Pro Tem Phan left the dais at 8:00 P.M. 
AGENDA ITEM NO. 17 WAS PULLED FOR SEPARATE DISCUSSION AND 
CONSIDERATION
